2026-05-15T01:15:21.4173556Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T01:15:21.4174447Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T01:15:21.4175332Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T01:15:21.4176240Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
